'''查·扎克·埃弗顿·弗雷德·阿當斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Che Zach Everton Fred Adams'''}}；{{bd|1996年|7月13日}}）是一位[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]足球運動員，場上司职[[中場_(足球)|中場]]和[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，現在效力於[[英超|英超]]球隊[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]，也代表[[蘇格蘭國家足球隊|苏格兰国家队]]參加国际比賽。

==球會生涯==
查·阿當斯在[[考文垂足球俱乐部|考文垂]]青年隊接受足球訓練，之後轉到[[伊爾基斯頓足球會|伊爾基斯頓]]繼續足球訓練<ref name=ifc /><ref>{{cite news|title=Sheffield United beat off Premier League competition to sign Ilkeston starlet Che Adams|url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/sheff-utd/sheffield-united-beat-off-premier-league-competition-to-sign-ilkeston-starlet-che-adams-1-6953957|accessdate=16 December 2014|newspaper=Sheffield Star|date=15 November 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220045407/http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/sheff-utd/sheffield-united-beat-off-premier-league-competition-to-sign-ilkeston-starlet-che-adams-1-6953957|archive-date=2014-12-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="but who">{{cite news|title=Che Adams' two goals stunned Tottenham, but who is Sheffield United's teen sensation who lit up Capital One Cup semi-final?|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2930596/Che-Adams-two-goals-stunned-Tottenham-Sheffield-United-s-teen-sensation.html|accessdate=29 January 2015|newspaper=Daily Mail|date=28 January 2015|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222745/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2930596/Che-Adams-two-goals-stunned-Tottenham-Sheffield-United-s-teen-sensation.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年11月14日，英甲球會[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|谢菲尔德联]]擊敗了其它高聯賽組別球會，簽下阿當斯，合約期兩年<ref name="nov sufc">{{cite news|title=Sheffield United: Che Adams joins Blades from Ilkeston|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30055438|accessdate=16 December 2014|publisher=BBC Sport|date=14 November 2014|archive-date=2014-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141118013647/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30055438|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Blades land non-league star|url=http://www.sufc.co.uk/news/article/20141114-che-adams-2084181.aspx|accessdate=16 December 2014|publisher=Sheffield United F.C.|date=14 November 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530013931/http://www.sufc.co.uk/news/article/20141114-che-adams-2084181.aspx|archive-date=2016-05-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。同年12月16日是他首場職業比賽的日子，對[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|南安普顿]]一戰中在半場換入[[亚马尔·坎贝尔-莱斯|亚马尔·坎贝尔-莱斯]]，最終谢菲尔德联獲勝並打進[[英格蘭足球聯賽盃|足球聯賽盃]]半決賽<ref>{{cite news|title=Sheffield United sink Southampton thanks to Marc McNulty’s goal|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/dec/16/sheffield-united-southampton-capital-one-cup-match-report|accessdate=16 December 2014|newspaper=The Guardian|date=16 December 2014|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130003449/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/dec/16/sheffield-united-southampton-capital-one-cup-match-report|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4天後他首次在[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]上場，在[[布拉莫巷体育场|布拉莫巷体育场]]對[[沃尔索尔足球俱乐部|沃尔索尔]]一戰中先發出場<ref>{{cite news|title=Sheff Utd 1–1 Walsall|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30459601|accessdate=28 January 2015|publisher=BBC Sport|date=20 December 2014|archive-date=2015-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120124208/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30459601|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年1月聯賽盃半決賽對主場[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|热刺]]一役，他在74分鐘替補上場，5分鐘後打進首顆職業入球，3分鐘後再打進第二球。最終[[克里斯蒂安·埃里克森|埃里克森]]在88分為熱刺打進一球，使熱刺總比數以3-2勝出<ref name="who is he">{{cite news|title=Che Adams: He scored twice in three minutes, but who is he?|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/31034225|accessdate=29 January 2015|publisher=BBC Newsbeat|date=29 January 2015}}</ref><ref name="but who" /><ref>{{cite news|title=Sheff Utd 2–2 Tottenham|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30910040|accessdate=29 January 2015|publisher=BBC Sport|date=28 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130082340/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30910040|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

阿當斯該季共替球隊在聯賽上場10次，球隊在晉級附加賽區完成聯賽。晉級附加賽半決場第二輪對[[斯温登足球俱乐部|斯温登]]，他在完場前5分鐘入替[[瑞安·弗林|瑞安·弗林]]並打進一球追成5-5平手，但總比數以7-6落敗<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hassan|first1=Nabil|title=Swindon 5–5 Sheff Utd|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32579316|accessdate=11 May 2015|publisher=BBC Sport|date=11 May 2015|archive-date=2015-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714234337/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32579316|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年8月15日，阿當斯打進首顆及第二顆聯賽進球，以2-0擊敗[[切斯特菲尔德足球俱乐部|切斯特菲尔德]]取得賽季首勝<ref>{{cite news|title=Sheff Utd 2-0 Chesterfield|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33831839|accessdate=16 August 2015|publisher=BBC Sport|date=15 August 2015|archive-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001033911/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/33831839|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10天後，他簽下為期三年的新合約，外加一年球會延長權<ref>{{cite news|title=Che Adams: Sheffield United striker signs new contract|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34051143|accessdate=25 August 2015|publisher=BBC Sport|date=25 August 2015}}</ref>。12月5日[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]對[[奥尔德姆足球俱乐部|奥尔德姆]]的賽事，他因為一次侵犯而取得直接紅牌離場<ref>{{cite news|title=Oldham 1-0 Sheff Utd|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34950937|accessdate=5 December 2015|publisher=BBC Sport|date=5 December 2015|archive-date=2015-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151217181332/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/34950937|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015/16球季，他共在聯賽上場36次並打進11球。

===伯明翰城===
2016年8月8日，替谢菲尔德联上場1次後，他與英冠球會[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰]]簽約加盟，為期三年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/2016-17/official-che-adams-joins-blues-3234399.aspx |title=Official: Che Adams joins Blues |publisher=Birmingham City F.C. |date=8 August 2016 |accessdate=8 August 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170127025911/http://www.bcfc.com/news/article/2016-17/official-che-adams-joins-blues-3234399.aspx |archive-date=2017-01-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。阿當斯在8月16日作客對[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|威根]]賽事場首次代表伯明翰上場，在下半場入替並以1-1完場。下輪對[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]的[[同城德比|德比]]戰，他以先發身份上場並先開紀錄，可惜最終以3-1戰敗<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/match-reports/birmingham-city-1-wolves-3-11776956 |title=Birmingham City 1 Wolves 3: Che Adams debut goal counts for nothing in derby defeat |first=Brian |last=Dick |newspaper=Birmingham Mail |date=20 August 2016 |accessdate=21 August 2016 |archive-date=2019-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206203538/https://www.birminghammail.co.uk/sport/football/match-reports/birmingham-city-1-wolves-3-11776956 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
阿當斯父親是[[安地卡島|安地卡島]]人，他曾獲邀代表[[安提瓜和巴布達國家足球隊|安提瓜和巴布達]]出戰[[2014年加勒比海盃|2014年加勒比海盃]]，但拒絕了安提瓜和巴布達的邀請<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.derbytelegraph.co.uk/ilkeston-teenager-turns-chance-play-antigua-amp/story-23054011-detail/story.html |title=Ilkeston teenager turns down chance to play for Antigua & Barbuda |newspaper=Derby Telegraph |date=7 October 2014 |accessdate=27 October 2016 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113194020/http://www.derbytelegraph.co.uk/Ilkeston-teenager-turns-chance-play-Antigua-amp/story-23054011-detail/story.html |archivedate=2015年1月13日 }}</ref>。他亦獲由曾職業球員組成的[[英格蘭足球代表丙隊|英格蘭C隊]]邀請出戰<ref>{{cite news|title=Sheffield United: Young prospect gets his chance to shine|url=http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/sheff-utd/sheffield-united-young-prospect-gets-his-chance-to-shine-1-6981879|accessdate=16 December 2014|publisher=Sheffield Star|date=2 December 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220044953/http://www.thestar.co.uk/sport/sheff-utd/sheffield-united-young-prospect-gets-his-chance-to-shine-1-6981879|archive-date=2014-12-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但因為他與職業球會谢菲尔德联簽約加盟，使他不能出賽。2015年9月，阿當斯被[[英格蘭20歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U20]]徵召參加對被[[捷克20歲以下國家足球隊|捷克U20]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Veevers |first=Nicholas |title=England U20s squad selected ahead of Czech test |url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2015/aug/u20s-squad-named-for-czech-republic-270815 |accessdate=5 December 2015 |publisher=The Football Association |date=27 August 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6jbm4w51k?url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2015/aug/u20s-squad-named-for-czech-republic-270815 |archivedate=2016年8月8日 }}</ref>。首次上場是主戰5-0大勝一役，在未段17分後入替[[泰勒·沃克|泰勒·沃克]]<ref>{{cite web |title=England U20s kick-off with 5–0 win at St. George's Park |url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2015/sep/u20s-czech-republic-sgp-050915 |first=Nicholas |last=Veevers |accessdate=5 December 2015 |publisher=The Football Association |date=5 September 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6jbmc3e07?url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2015/sep/u20s-czech-republic-sgp-050915 |archivedate=2016年8月8日  }}</ref>，作客一戰則是先發成員出戰，1-0敗北而回<ref>{{cite web |title=England U20s fall to narrow defeat in Shrewsbury |url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2015/sep/england-u20s-czech-republic-match-report |publisher=The Football Association |date=7 September 2015 |accessdate=8 August 2016 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6jbpUnYk2?url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2015/sep/england-u20s-czech-republic-match-report |archivedate=2016年8月8日 }}</ref>。

2021年3月25日，在[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭]]對陣[[奧地利國家足球隊|奧地利]]的[[2022年國際足總世界盃外圍賽_(歐洲區)|2022年世界盃外圍賽]]中，亞當斯於第66分鐘替換[[斯圖爾特·阿姆斯特朗|斯圖爾特·阿姆斯特朗]]出場，完成國家隊首秀。<ref>{{cite news|title=John McGinn's superb volley rescues point for Scotland against Austria|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2021/mar/25/scotland-austria-world-cup-2022-qualifier-match-report|publisher=The Guardian|date=2021-03-25|accessdate=2021-03-26|archive-date=2021-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331164240/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2021/mar/25/scotland-austria-world-cup-2022-qualifier-match-report|dead-url=no}}</ref>並在六天后以4-0戰勝[[法羅群島足球代表隊|法羅群島]]的比賽中踢入了在蘇格蘭的第一個國際進球。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2021/03/31/scotland-vs-faroe-islands-world-cup-2022-qualifier-live-score/ |title=Che Adams scores first international goal as Scotland put four past the Faroe Islands |last1=Forsyth |first1=Roddy |last2=Bull |first2=J. J. |website=The Telegraph |date=2021-03-31 |access-date=2021-04-02 |archive-date=2021-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210331223025/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2021/03/31/scotland-vs-faroe-islands-world-cup-2022-qualifier-live-score/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

